job.title: CSIR-NAL Technician Recruitment 2021 – Apply online for 34 vacancies in Bengaluru
job.body:
Total Vacancies: 34

Name of the Vacancies:

  • Technician

Description

Latest Central Government Jobs for the 10th pass has been published by National Aerospace Laboratories for Technician vacancies in Bengaluru. If you are searching for a government job in Bengaluru then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the vacancies of Technician, from the 20.04.2021, and till the 06.06.2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in Bengaluru and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.

Application fee:

  • The mode of application is Online
  • No information about application fee

Educational qualification:

  • To apply for a Technician in CSIR-NAL, your 10th must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates:

  •  The starting date to apply in these posts is the 20.04.2021
  •  The last date to apply in these posts is 06.06.2021

Age Limit Criteria:

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 18 to 28 years old. 

CSIR-NAL Technician Pay Scale:

  • According to the information given by the Central Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is ₹ 31,000

How to apply for CSIR-NAL Technician Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the Technician. Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of CSIR-NAL and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by CSIR-NAL
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.

Download Official notification pdf.
